text: Abduqohir Abdurasulovich Nazirov (; born 8 March 1959) is a Tajik politician who is serving as the Prime Minister of Tajikistan since 23 November 2013. He is a member of the People's Democratic Party of Tajikistan. ==References== Category:1959 births Category:Living people Category:Prime ministers of Tajikistan
title: Kokhir Rasulzoda
